---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="Support | LetsFixIndia" description="Ways to support a source-led public record for India.">
  <div class="page-shell"><header class="record-header"><p class="eyebrow">Support the record</p><h1>Evidence is the most useful contribution.</h1><p class="lede">Share a source with the claim, submit a correction, or help check a public record. Those actions make this project more useful for everyone.</p></header>
    <div class="feature-grid section"><article class="intent-card"><span class="intent-icon" aria-hidden="true">1</span><h3>Share responsibly</h3><p>Share a specific record and its sources, rather than a claim without context.</p><a href="/timeline">Explore the record →</a></article><article class="intent-card"><span class="intent-icon" aria-hidden="true">2</span><h3>Improve an entry</h3><p>Send a stronger source, corrected wording, date, number, or court outcome.</p><a href="/submit">Suggest a correction →</a></article><article class="intent-card"><span class="intent-icon" aria-hidden="true">3</span><h3>Contribute openly</h3><p>Inspect the project data or code and help make the evidence trail more complete.</p><a href="https://github.com/basithladdu/letsfixindia" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Open GitHub ↗</a></article></div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
